metadata.name: The VITO 100A
metadata.description:
The VITO 100A comes with a single, beautifully crafted button - the only button you'll ever need for a fulfilling and fruitful artistic career. The moment you press that knob, VITO 100A instantly creates a fresh, emotional, incredibly impactful cutting-edge artwork, so good that you'd think it was made by Rick Vito himself.¹

Here's what paid actors say about it in a blind test:
Sarah (62): "Well, I don't know, it probably makes art like you said. It's hard to tell without being able to see it. Oops, I think I pressed a button or something."

Tanner (19):  "I've heard it has healing powers, but my mom says it makes art.² I guess art can heal or whatever but I've never had that happen to me, so. Can I take the blindfold off?"

¹ The art is in fact made by Rick Vitos from parallel universes and covertly acquired. Copyright does not extend across The Multiverse.
² The VITO 100A does not have healing powers, it only covertly acquires or "creates" art.

---
Rick Vito, August 2022
DALL·E 2
